---
description: Best practices for using Tailwind CSS in React applications
globs: src/**/*.tsx,src/**/*.css
alwaysApply: false
---

- Use utility-first classes for styling components
- Create custom components with Tailwind classes for reusability
- Utilize responsive design utilities for mobile-first development
- DO NOT implement dark mode support using Tailwind's dark mode classes
- Use only the variables that are already defined in the project
